title: Chicago Playing Cards - Red Deck
description:
Suitable for people who like to play cards a little or a lot. The design of the entire deck is based on a classic playing card look with a definitive Chicago twist featuring notable Chicagoans and are printed on casino quality 310gsm linen card stock.

  • Kings: Richard Daley, Barack Obama, Mike Ditka, Michael Jordan
  • Queens: Jane Addams, Oprah Winfrey, Chaka Khan, Jane Byrne
  • Jacks: Al Capone, Harold Washington, Muddy Waters, Harry Caray
  • Joker: Bill Murray
  • Ace of Spades: Statue of Republic
